bilingual.target: 他们的公司在海外有很多分支机构。

bilingual.source: The product is very popular in overseas markets.
bilingual.target: 这款产品在海外市场非常受欢迎。

bilingual.source: This product is very popular in overseas markets.
bilingual.target: 这个产品在海外市场很受欢迎。

bilingual.source: Her father is currently on active service overseas.
bilingual.target: 她的父亲目前正在海外服役。

bilingual.source: The serviceman was stationed overseas for two years.
bilingual.target: 军人在海外驻扎了两年。

bilingual.source: Their sales in the overseas market increased by 20%.
bilingual.target: 他们在海外市场的销售额增长了20%。

bilingual.source: The company is nominally based in London, but most of its operations are overseas.
bilingual.target: 这家公司名义上地设在伦敦，但大部分业务在海外。

bilingual.source: The overseas ATM and your debit card.
bilingual.target: 考虑是否能在海外的提款机上使用你的银行卡。

bilingual.source: But most of its products are made overseas.
bilingual.target: 但是，其大多数产品都在海外制造。

list.abstract: overseas（英 [ˌəʊvəˈsiːz]，美 [ˌoʊvərˈsiːz]），英语单词，作副词时，为在国外；向国外。作形容词时，为来自国外的；去国外的。短语搭配有overseas market（海外市场）。例句为“People were excited to go travelling overseas.（人们对去海外旅行感到兴奋。）” overseas副词类近义词有beyond the sea，形容词类近义词有transmarine、off-shore。

yingyinNormal.en: Today, we are grateful to all Americans who do their part to live by those ideals including our brave men and women in uniform overseas and their families who sacrifice so much to keep America safe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天，我们感恩所有做出自己的努力，靠这些理想生活的所有国人，包括我们远在海外英勇的男女军人以及他们的家人，是他们的牺牲保证了美国的安全。

yingyinNormal.en: How's that, sir? They felt it. Whatever happened to you overseas, there's no reason to feel guilty or ashamed. I served my country. I did what I did because it's what I had to do. Not like some others.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么说，先生。他们察觉出来了。无论你在海外有过什么遭遇，你都不必感到内疚或惭愧。我为国尽忠了，我那么做是因为我别无选择。不像某些人。

yingyinNormal.en: 80% of the town worked for the textile factory, but business was moving overseas.
yingyinNormal.zh: 镇上80%的人都在纺织厂工作，但公司要搬到海外了。

yingyinNormal.en: Lord Moran, Peer of the Realm. Minister for Overseas Development. Pillar of the Establishment.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莫兰爵士，上议院成员，海外发展部大臣，上层建筑之一。

yingyinNormal.en: A customer service representative with an Indian accent will create the impression we're a vast enterprise that uses overseas call centers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个操着印度口音的客服能够给客人们留下一种我们这是跨国公司使用海外客服中心的印象。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It must rely on low-wage <highlight>overseas</highlight> labor, order in volumes that strain natural resources, and use massive amounts of harmful chemicals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它必须依靠廉价的海外劳动力，大批量订货以致过度消耗自然资源，并且还要使用大量的有害化学物质。
